{"tid":808141,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入)手足口病的第三日","createTime":"2018-09-06T06:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:11:24.000Z","uid":34872,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"896ad77a8d5b875b011099b21143658e509b51d3","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mz9scb0r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmz9scb0r&h=b1f504da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sdnzgrf7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsdnzgrf7&h=916ed934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇手足知仲有幾耐會甩曬焦<br />\n而家好似仲有新豆豆爆緊出黎<br />\n手停口停 而家做緊餐廳洗碗 冇sick leave 想知幾耐會好 <br />\n唉屌 好撚憎份工 可能因為唔戴手套掂d下欄碟搞到咁 屌你老味 而家仲要成星期冇人工 <br />\n醫生9 up 兩句 又收我65蚊澳幣 止痛藥都唔開<br />\n第一日d 粒粒爆緊出黎 痛苦程度去到level 5"},{"pid":"2315c0e3975ca202760588a790e4d5b5cd564f07","tid":808141,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"兒登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成人好似好少野到，你咁唔好彩"},{"pid":"88d5b4977c04c18104249a16757315a26122dab1","tid":808141,"uid":171901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"梅毒"},{"pid":"2c6bf7c1584ef8a792a4c4f0ffcfeb6bdb58ef27","tid":808141,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"未好返唔好開工<br />\n一係講明係邊到開工"},{"pid":"356fdf6080e3992bacf6f2813ac95ee7c33aa103","tid":808141,"uid":22048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔似手足口病喎<br />\n口有冇生飛滋？腳板底有冇生粒粒？<br />\n我果時係手同腳有少少粒粒 口有差唔多10粒唔識好既飛滋<br />\n好似仲有少少燒既會<br />\n但你生得咁嚴重唔係好似手足口喎"},{"pid":"559fcee943fdc3d51b4b2e63eece3d1684c53a09","tid":808141,"uid":101845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"我上次手足口病唔係咁喎"},{"pid":"ee0ce224e33046b1c9a87d26951a45f1f845d706","tid":808141,"uid":52719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"如果唔似手足口似咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968d8934e3424d4e4a53126d295e1bc260d452bc","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔似手足口病喎<br />\n口有冇生飛滋？腳板底有冇生粒粒？<br />\n我果時係手同腳有少少粒粒 口有差唔多10粒唔識好既飛滋<br />\n好似仲有少少燒既會<br />\n但你生得咁嚴重唔係好似手足口喎</blockquote><br />\n腳得幾粒 JJ附近都有<br />\n口腔冇飛之 但喉嚨入面有 頭一日每次食野都好似吞刀片咁"},{"pid":"20475e18db1f26fdc3a8976b0a4df46b9128b14d","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅毒</blockquote><br />\n上次call g 都是一年前既事<br />\n唔是貢好彩下話"},{"pid":"729f60650ebbbcf0b62219e5a86a4385d3e18519","tid":808141,"uid":35307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"導致手足口病的病毒會藉由皮膚接觸、糞口傳染或飛沫的方式散播。 患者碰觸過的物品也具有傳染力。<br />\n<br />\n但真係關洗碗事？<br />\n諗唔到啲碗點樣傳播手足口病"},{"pid":"60a7a3bd0bc1bac7daf1fa37ec501d811de092a6","tid":808141,"uid":79839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"聯醫生無講咩病？"},{"pid":"643ff4545c351f744739e3be23e407f576432e0e","tid":808141,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"大病係外國睇醫生 姐係等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df0551d7978120f78e66af8a0639b107964a1a3","tid":808141,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"想奶"},{"pid":"4fec62f3dabfd68fd7cf220761fe62871078ba3a","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導致手足口病的病毒會藉由皮膚接觸、糞口傳染或飛沫的方式散播。 患者碰觸過的物品也具有傳染力。<br />\n<br />\n但真係關洗碗事？<br />\n諗唔到啲碗點樣傳播手足口病</blockquote><br />\n可能是細路嘔吐物<br />\n餐廳用下欄盤將檯上既野掃曬入去<br />\n我就要用手響入面汁番d碗碟黎洗"},{"pid":"7940f3d9bd5f27c6a9959da9d9e79cc86c127574","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聯醫生無講咩病？</blockquote><br />\n佢話係手足口"},{"pid":"622b74dd398f4614f0d9d3cfc47819571ef461a0","tid":808141,"uid":31198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7940f3d9bd5f27c6a9959da9d9e79cc86c127574","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聯醫生無講咩病？</blockquote><br />\n佢話係手足口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"唔似手足口病喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣我只係手同腳出細細粒紅點 成個喉嚨生哂飛滋<br />\n絕對無你隻手咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如睇下第二個醫生講咩"},{"pid":"110056a4348245e4fce9d6faf1447eb4ce50664b","tid":808141,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"jj附近無理由會有<br />\n手足紅點，喉嚨痛到仆街<br />\n頭兩日會發燒<br />\n<br />\n你隻手既嚴重程度好誇張<br />\n你去睇多次醫生同佢講唔止手同腳有啦"},{"pid":"32175871299dac7ea2cbce591bd01b2ddcfe3fcc","tid":808141,"uid":23532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"我就似出水豆，但係就痛到仆街好成千支針吉咁痛"},{"pid":"c62b3fa76916c66d24f93624bcb24551518f7630","tid":808141,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就似出水豆，但係就痛到仆街好成千支針吉咁痛</blockquote><br />\n頭一日既感受 我狂啪Panadol 係痛到仆街<br />\n果日淩晨每兩個鐘痛醒一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6119381c62214e25dfc1e855c7ea005e6dbe1c6","tid":808141,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"搵多個醫生睇睇好 唔好慳呢D錢  <br />\n加油! 希望你早日康復"},{"pid":"87b71c513b1db2ccc787a00975bde2f